Self-modifying code is a code that modyfies itself through execution (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Self-modifying_code)
JIT (RuiJIT) is already a sort of self-modifying code. RuiJIT + Roslyin in general already have all required infrastructure to create advanced self-modifying code.

Primary target:
1) Event-loop with specialized event invocation.
``` CSharp 
/// ------------------ Tradiltional event loop example: ---------------------------------
